INSERT INTO `submit_test_writing` VALUES (1,'2025-06-03 21:37:27.029160',_binary '','2025-06-03 21:37:56.198669','Error processing writing sample: Error checking text with LanguageTool: I/O error on POST request for \"http://localhost:8081/v2/check\": Connection refused','I usually wake up at 6:30 AM every morning and start my day with a cup of coffee. I always check my emails and read the news while having breakfast. After that, I take the bus to work because it is more convenient than driving. I work as a marketing manager, and my office hours are from 9:00 AM to 5:30 PM. During lunch break, I often eat with my colleagues at a nearby restaurant.\nHowever, this week I am doing things quite differently. I am currently working from home because my office is being renovated. I am also taking an online course in digital marketing, so I am spending extra hours studying in the evenings. My schedule is more flexible now, and I am enjoying the change of pace. I am waking up a bit later than usual and having more time for breakfast.\nIn the afternoons, I am attending virtual meetings with clients and am learning new software programs. I am also cooking more meals at home instead of eating out. This temporary change is teaching me to be more organized with my time, and I am discovering that I am actually more productive when working from home.',0,5,17),(2,'2025-06-03 21:37:42.961287',_binary '','2025-06-03 21:37:56.223956','Error processing writing sample: Error checking text with LanguageTool: I/O error on POST request for \"http://localhost:8081/v2/check\": Connection refused','\nI have experienced many significant changes in my life that have shaped who I am today. Five years ago, I have moved to a new city to pursue my university education, and this decision has completely transformed my perspective on life. I have met people from different cultural backgrounds and have learned to be more open-minded and tolerant.\nDuring my university years, I have joined several student organizations and have developed strong leadership skills. I have also traveled to three different countries, which has broadened my understanding of the world. Recently, I have completed my degree in business administration and have started my first professional job. These experiences have taught me the importance of perseverance and hard work.\nAll these life changes now influence how I approach daily challenges. I believe that every experience teaches us valuable lessons, and I always try to learn something new from difficult situations. I am more confident in my abilities now because I have overcome many obstacles in the past. My travels have made me appreciate different cultures, so I enjoy working in diverse environments. The leadership experience I have gained helps me communicate effectively with my colleagues and manage projects successfully.',0,5,18),(3,'2025-06-03 21:37:50.107857',_binary '','2025-06-03 21:37:56.249406','Error processing writing sample: Error checking text with LanguageTool: I/O error on POST request for \"http://localhost:8081/v2/check\": Connection refused','I am currently working on several exciting projects that are helping me grow professionally. I am developing a new marketing campaign for our company\'s latest product launch, and I am collaborating with a team of creative designers. We are also conducting market research to better understand our target audience.\nIn my personal life, I am learning Spanish through online classes and am practicing with native speakers twice a week. I am also training for a half-marathon that will take place next month, so I am running five kilometers every other day.\nRecently, I have completed a professional certification in project management, which has already improved my job performance. I have also started volunteering at a local animal shelter, and this experience has been incredibly rewarding. I have made new friends through this volunteer work and have learned about animal care.\nLooking