:18.745540',_binary '','2025-06-01 20:24:18.745549','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/toeic/part2/audio/part2-temp-9a6795a3-59f4-45c6-b05f-36cf6fb6b60a','B','M-Au Where is the parking garage?(A) The local park is nice.(B) Behind the office building.(C) During his commute to work'),(102,'2025-06-01 20:28:13.352807',_binary '','2025-06-01 20:28:13.352815','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/toeic/part2/audio/part2-temp-4a8a32ed-e5cf-472f-b305-7a22d39289b1','B','W-Br When will the design team meet?(A) No, I ordered five.(B) Sometime next month.(C) On top of the cabinet.'),(103,'2025-06-01 20:28:33.176057',_binary '','2025-06-01 20:28:33.176072','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/toeic/part2/audio/part2-temp-56824923-74be-41d4-9ba2-6547812409b6','A','W-Am Should we consider Anita for the accountant position?(A) Yes, we\'re reviewing her application now.(B) Down the hall to the right.(C) The box is open.'),(104,'2025-06-01 20:28:51.845224',_binary '','2025-06-01 20:28:51.845230','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/toeic/part2/audio/part2-temp-8a1bc7e5-fe9a-407d-a526-2e4fd2a2f49b','B','M-Cn What are they building near the shopping center?(A) On the eighteenth floor.(B) An apartment complex.(C) I shop there on the weekends.'),(105,'2025-06-01 20:29:14.445251',_binary '','2025-06-01 20:29:14.445257','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/toeic/part2/audio/part2-temp-ecc26975-ced9-4549-8640-4f08a1a38d84','C','W-Am How did you like the meal?(A) I like that idea.(B) By taxicab.(C) It was excellent.'),(106,'2025-06-01 20:29:43.534447',_binary '','2025-06-01 20:29:43.534454','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/toeic/part2/audio/part2-temp-2c7d2668-7ab3-4a7f-bb5f-91af3ebaf9a4','B','W-Br Why did the manager e-mail you?(A) Yes, I\'m sure.(B) Because she wants me to work late.(C) Do you have any stamps?'),(107,'2025-06-01 20:30:12.037180',_binary '','2025-06-01 20:30:12.037186','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/toeic/part2/audio/part2-temp-79fe5607-f993-484c-ac59-2da