6:31.945544',_binary '','2025-06-01 16:16:31.945567','Please sit on the chair while waiting.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/0-c3bba97c-98a8-4503-9a1a-66b47a3642c6','Ghế','/tʃer/','Chair','NOUN',2),(9,'2025-06-01 16:20:44.944623',_binary '','2025-06-01 16:20:44.944640','They bought a new leather sofa for the living room.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/0-bbe09e03-8751-43fb-b3fd-b97828fe8af9','Ghế sofa','/ˈsəʊ.fə/','Sofa','NOUN',2),(10,'2025-06-01 16:21:34.823813',_binary '','2025-06-01 16:21:34.823826','She turned on the lamp to read her book.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/0-0edc9172-d443-4b87-936e-60a7d139dd37','Đèn','/læmp/','Lamp','NOUN',2),(11,'2025-06-01 16:22:18.479812',_binary '','2025-06-01 16:22:18.479824','He looked at himself in the mirror before leaving.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/0-8acb0d55-67c3-4327-b141-d8ad96afafa1','Gương','/ˈmɪr.ər/','Mirror','NOUN',2),(12,'2025-06-01 16:23:55.918580',_binary '','2025-06-01 16:23:55.918607','All her favorite novels are on the bookshelf.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/0-ae390901-aed2-4a30-b3ae-864c51bf76e2','Kệ sách','/ˈbʊk.ʃelf/','Bookshelf','NOUN',2),(13,'2025-06-01 16:25:34.325859',_binary '','2025-06-01 16:25:34.325872','The energy drink is inside the refrigerator.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/0-d3b79d35-b149-4c70-9fec-5c03143ef81b','Tủ lạnh','/rɪˈfrɪdʒ.ə.reɪ.tər/','Refrigerator','NOUN',2),(14,'2025-06-01 16:26:23.114111',_binary '','2025-06-01 16:26:23.114123','She keeps her clothes neatly in the wardrobe.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/0-7d31be10-fc8a-4a92-a062-548fb300d3a2','Tủ quần áo','/ˈwɔːr.droʊb/','Wardrobe','NOUN',2),(15,'2025-06-01 16:36:22.213447',_binary '','2025-06-01 16:36:22.213468','\"Good morning!\" is a friendly greeting.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/0-3248b0ea-3234-470c-a8a4-211165d6d3d8','Lời chào','/ˈɡriː.tɪŋ/','Greeting','NOUN',3),(16,'2025-06-01 16:37:03.708316',_binary '','2025-06-01 16:37:03.708329','\"Hi, my name is Anna\" is a simple introduction.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/0-0b56f78b-1293-48af-bbbb-059b2d0668a5','Giới thiệu','/ˌɪn.trəˈdʌk.ʃən/','Introduction','NOUN',3),(17,'2025-06-01 16:41:04.698489',_binary '','2025-06-01 16:44:40.007551','\"I\'m sorry for being late\" is an apology.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/17-72e5aa4d-72fd-48cf-a4d6-41e96928a069','Lời xin lỗi','/əˈpɒl.ə.dʒi/','Apology','NOUN',3),(18,'2025-06-01 16:42:24.955092',_binary '','2025-06-01 16:42:24.955103','We need to communicate clearly to avoid misunderstandings.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/0-4cf23d96-21aa-44ab-a681-4d0576121fe0','Giao tiếp','/kəˈmjuː.nɪ.keɪt/','Communicate','VERB',3),(19,'2025-06-01 16:44:29.285344',_binary '','2025-06-01 16:47:40.132794','It’s rude to interrupt someone while they’re speaking.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/19-dc5a11bf-87a3-4c29-a243-fa84e26cbb82','Ngắt lời','/ˌɪn.təˈrʌpt/','Interrupt','VERB',3),(20,'2025-06-01 16:45:27.731329',_binary '','2025-06-01 16:45:27.731341','She tried to persuade her boss to give her a raise.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/0-6f3688d0-a688-4cf6-9a46-d6899bae2a55','Thuyết phục','/pərˈsweɪd/','Persuade','VERB',3),(21,'2025-06-01 16:47:15.711687',_binary '','2025-06-01 16:47:15.711698',' He gave a polite answer to the difficult question.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/0-017604b0-238e-4f9d-ba87-45c45e1b7f1a','Lịch sự','/pəˈlaɪt/','Polite','ADJECTIVE',3),(22,'2025-06-01 16:49:10.515206',_binary '','2025-06-01 16:51:17.174428','They whispered secrets to each other during the movie.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/22-0a743c32-9205-4095-8ef1-42b506e71062','Thì thầm','/ˈwɪs.pər/','Whisper','VERB',3),(23,'2025-06-01 16:51:10.334189',_binary '','2025-06-01 16:57:02.010171','Please speak clearly so everyone can understand.','http:/