-01 18:09:35.429189','She ended the letter with \"Sincerely yours\".','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/0-53654a93-3f33-40fa-bc5c-ede30abf043d','Chân thành','/sɪnˈsɪr.li/','Sincerely','ADVERB',4),(32,'2025-06-01 18:09:57.124444',_binary '','2025-06-01 18:09:57.124458','Reply to important emails promptly.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/0-2438d013-2e5b-41df-b96a-483442f34cd9','Ngay lập tức','/ˈprɒmpt.li/','Promptly','ADVERB',4),(33,'2025-06-01 18:12:54.697258',_binary '','2025-06-01 18:12:54.697271','Write a clear subject line for your email.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/0-bc50ab6d-7e7f-4efc-bde3-12e289b6ec61','Dòng tiêu đề','/ˈsʌb.dʒekt laɪn/','Subject line','NOUN',4),(34,'2025-06-01 18:13:12.833804',_binary '','2025-06-01 18:13:12.833815','He closed the email with \"Best regards\".','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/vocabulary/0-9b7741be-822f-4173-830a-558f89cc0665','Trân trọng','/best rɪˈɡɑːrdz/','Best regards','NOUN',4);
