INSERT INTO `writing` VALUES (1,'2025-05-17 10:23:41.138163',_binary '','2025-06-03 17:22:01.905438','In this lesson, you will write about recycle','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/writing/-1-3d4ab42f-d0f2-4d9c-9cf3-887fe8efef33','Recycle',0,'http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/writing/1-12834d5a-71af-4cfd-875c-234b0da50b76','Recycling in my house separating paper, plastic, and glass. We labeled bins and compost food waste. This small effort helps protect our environment for future generations.','Recycle in your house',NULL,3),(2,'2025-06-02 15:41:39.331196',_binary '','2025-06-04 09:36:59.093605','This lesson helps students improve their English writing skills by focusing on local environmental pollution issues. Students will learn relevant vocabulary, practice sentence structure, and write a short paragraph.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/writing/2-b87dc80b-0f8d-4ce2-a875-df3adf636226','Local Environmental Pollution',2,'http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/writing/2-e66b2f1b-249b-4163-8e34-58344f18a591','Pollution is a serious in many cities. Factories release harmful into the air, and people often throw on the streets. To reduce pollution, we should more and use energy sources like solar power.','How Can Students Help Reduce Pollution in Their Community?',NULL,15),(3,'2025-06-02 15:49:34.505168',_binary '','2025-06-03 17:13:10.279475','This lesson helps students learn how to confidently introduce themselves in English, covering basic personal information, hobbies, and daily routines.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/writing/3-18f62a83-3a74-4711-9ed7-fb016f35319a','Introducing Yourself',0,'http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/writing/3-121fd707-1ad5-4801-9dd5-8e113aeeb46a','My is David. I am 30 years , and I come Canada. I work as a in the hospitalhospital. In my free time, I like  books and watching movies.','Introduce yourself in front of the crowd',NULL,16),(4,'2025-06-02 15:56:59.494047',_binary '','2025-06-03 17:14:16.723021','This lesson teaches students how to describe their daily work routines in English, using proper time expressions and action verbs.','http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/writing/4-37a88680-039b-46d2-84cc-4b36a6c52ecb','Daily Work Schedule',0,'http://138.2.91.94:9000/h2t-english/writing/4-fb8782f6-60ad-47bd-81ad-e9ed58278383','I up at 6:30 AM every weekday. First, I breakfast and ready for work. My work at 8:00 AM. I usually my most important tasks in the morning.','Describe Your Ideal Workday',NULL,17);
